知名研究机构报告：新冠疫情对全球经济影响集中在上半年。
Leading research groups report that the impact of the new crown epidemic on the global economy is concentrated in the first half of the year.
李静。
Li Jing.
中国新闻周刊                      。
China News Weekly.
